data.description: This stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath ranch home is an absolute must-see! Nestled in the highly sought-after Reid Plantation Subdivision in the charming town of Villa Rica, this home offers an unparalleled living experience. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious master suite, complete with a cozy sitting room and not one, but two master closets. Imagine waking up each morning and sipping your favorite coffee on the enclosed back porch, overlooking the serene beauty of your fenced-in yard adorned with majestic pine trees. As you make your way through the home, you'll be captivated by the warmth and ambiance of the gas fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings spent curled up with a good book or enjoying quality time with loved ones. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this extraordinary home yours. With its undeniable charm and desirable location, it won't stay on the market for long. Schedule your showing today and prepare to fall in love with your dream home.
